<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA5">
<l>iṟaivaṉē yevvuyirun tōṟṟuvippāṉ ṟōṟṟi</l>
<l>yiṟaivaṉē yīṇṭiṟakkañ ceyvā - ṉiṟaivaṉē</l>
<l>yentā yeṉaviraṅku meṅkaḷmēl ventuyaram</l>
<l>vantā latumāṟṟu vāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The lord, he makes appear all life. Having made it appear,</l>
<l>the lord, he makes destruction here. The lord,</l>
<l>when hot misery comes upon us, who lament “o father”,</l>
<l>he will change that.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
